metadata.name: Self Love
metadata.description:
Self Love Potion

Ingredients: 

Green comet
Positive Affirmations 
Practice Self-Care 
Set Boundaries 
Daily Gratitude Ritual 
Health Consciousness 
Spiritual Practise 
Forgive Yourself


Each bottle houses the ingredients that embody the feeling of self love, passion, or the cosiness of a hearts warmth. Some of these potions scents are potent, some of them have unscented ingredients. All of them perfume the aura/sprit/soul of those who wear them. 

Each potion will smell different to the wearer, with notes that echo from personal memories, hopes and dreams.
